yTime":"2019-10-16T14:58:28.000Z","msg":"佢地發起預左係和理非，要尊重佢地，唔好辜負左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T15:03:10.000Z","msg":"多謝有岑子杰，同其他遊行發起人，仲有和理非同好多抗爭義士唔怕敵人攻擊傷害，勇敢企出黎。<br />\n過往被兇徒襲擊既手足，付出咗太多太多，我地實在無以為報。"},{"pid":"48fbd6c35acce67d8d9db5806957cca7e39b9f57","tid":1658700,"uid":215634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T15:04:56.000Z","msg":"我唔想沉底，求推"},{"pid":"c12d0b7fb5717ff847adb871d5d0ac56aa090452","tid":1658700,"uid":215634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T15:08:54.000Z","msg":"求推"},{"pid":"43323840096bd9d9aad7ea2e476b58ed723f5261","tid":1658700,"uid":215634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0afccf86ac9a077effe23bc6c60b65e9f4895032","tid":1658700,"uid":761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T14:53:13.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T15:13:22.000Z","msg":"跪求推多一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ef7a39b3a8cbe67eaa0dadb28559e4c56b65b27","tid":1658700,"uid":38122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T15:14:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"51e8764ea5e192c228248375fe84113aae13d942","tid":1658700,"uid":215634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c270375155a9eb806c616b2cb9f77c74349ff956","tid":1658700,"uid":8392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T14:57:34.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T15:15:25.000Z","msg":"我唔想po沉底，跪求你推多一下"},{"pid":"95224990d26333bba4f63af58f5f550c980460ac","tid":1658700,"uid":761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T15:23:51.000Z","msg":"推"}]}